{"tid":1774991,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"落得街，和勇都要保持危機意識","createTime":"2019-12-08T14:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T15:05:22.000Z","uid":207710,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"48f2a288ad23df1b42bd8c849c64187e1b9832e7","tid":1774991,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:35:31.000Z","msg":"今日啱啱開始嗰陣銅鑼灣已經出黑旗<br />\n但仍然見到有啲人擺晒pose打卡<br />\n有啲戴啲笨重嘅裝扮cosplay<br />\n啱先仲睇新聞見到話有fa同朋友扮被捕<br />\n<br />\n雖然今日有不反相對安全<br />\n但其實三點左右已經有黑旗<br />\n每個位置都隨時變前線隨時食彈<br />\n上個禮拜戴唔切裝嘅已經中招<br />\n<br />\n唔係話個個都要有gear咁誇<br />\n但起碼要有警剔有危機感<br />\n走嘅時候要走得郁be water<br />\n如果唔係相當危險<br />\n誇張啲甚至可能人踩人<br />\n<br />\n要稍為輕鬆啲多啲創意嘅表達<br />\n可以選擇定點嘅集會先做<br />\n例如「吸吸可危」、「親子集會」先做<br />\n會安全好多"},{"pid":"de39151606b5b6f4be092ada06ad631fd44c5edd","tid":1774991,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:38:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f23f632852a85470518eebb332eead28435a796","tid":1774991,"uid":37234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:39:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35caabdf5a85aea9d20f9b6ae346fd0b9879b07a","tid":1774991,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:39:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 遊行rt like reply</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">task1 英語外媒 </span>(大家盡情貼今日唔水同角度的遊行相落去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">task4 日韓及其他外語媒體</span>（急要人retweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=u6uLjzzFZj4TH%2F5rj7Ekc%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=bf208cbd\" data-auto-link targe